<TEXT type="Text" html="y" lines="7">Remember to set the field type to &lt;font color=&quot;#ff0000&quot;&gt;allow HTML rich text content&lt;/font&gt; when using formatting tags.  This is done in the &lt;font color=&quot;#0000ff&quot;&gt;&quot;Data-&gt;Configure Data Types-&gt;Field Type&quot;&lt;/font&gt; dialog.</TEXT>
</TEXT_PARA>
