<TOPIC ref="y">Bold Text</TOPIC>
<TEXT>Font tags can be applied from the &lt;b&gt;right-click context menu&lt;/b&gt; in the &quot;Data Editor&quot; view.</TEXT>
</TEXT_PARA>
